## 2.3

由

$$EA\frac{{{\partial ^2}U\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}} = - m{\omega ^2}U\left( x \right)$$

得

$$
\begin{array}{l}
EA\int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{U_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} = - m{\lambda _i}\int_0^L {{U_i}\left( x \right){U_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} \\
\left. {EA{U_j}\left( x \right)\frac{{\partial {U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}} \right|_0^L - EA\int_0^L {\frac{{\partial {U_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}\frac{{\partial {U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}{\rm{d}}x} = - m{\lambda _i}\int_0^L {{U_i}\left( x \right){U_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x}
\end{array}
$$

代入边界条件

$${\left. {{U_i}k{U_j}} \right|_{x = 0}} - EA\int_0^L {\frac{{\partial {U_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}\frac{{\partial {U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}{\rm{d}}x} = - m{\lambda _i}\int_0^L {{U_i}\left( x \right){U_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x}$$

同理

$$
{\left. {{U_j}k{U_i}} \right|_{x = 0}} - EA\int_0^L {\frac{{\partial {U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}\frac{{\partial {U_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}{\rm{d}}x} = - m{\lambda _j}\int_0^L {{U_j}\left( x \right){U_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x}
$$

所以

$$\left( {{\lambda _i} - {\lambda _j}} \right)\int_0^L {{U_i}\left( x \right)m{U_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} = 0$$

当${\lambda _i} \neq {\lambda _j}$,

$$\int_0^L {{U_i}\left( x \right)m{U_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} = 0$$

## 2.4

由

$$
\begin{array}{l}
\left\langle {M\left[ {{U_1}} \right],{U_1}} \right\rangle \approx 17.201mL\\
\left\langle {M\left[ {{U_2}} \right],{U_2}} \right\rangle \approx 76.458mL\\
\left\langle {M\left[ {{U_3}} \right],{U_3}} \right\rangle \approx 175.122mL
\end{array}
$$

得

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{c_1} = \frac{1}{{\sqrt {17.201mL} }}\\
{c_2} = \frac{1}{{\sqrt {76.458mL} }}\\
{c_3} = \frac{1}{{\sqrt {175.122mL} }}
\end{array}
$$

所以可设

$$u\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$$

代入可得

$$
m\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} - EA\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} = 0
$$

同时积分

$$
m\int_0^L {{U_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x} - EA\int_0^L {{U_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = 0
$$

可得

$$
{\ddot \eta _i} + \omega _i^2{\eta _i} = 0,{\rm{ }}i = 1,2,3
$$

解为

$$
\eta_i = C_{i1} \cos \omega t + C_{i2} \sin \omega t
$$

由

$$
\int_0^L {m{U_i}\left( x \right)u\left( {x,0} \right){\rm{d}}x} = \sum\limits_{j = 1}^3 {\int_0^L {m{U_i}{U_j}{\eta _j}\left( 0 \right){\rm{d}}x} }
$$

可得初始条件为

$$
{\eta _i}\left( 0 \right) = \int_0^L {m{U_i}\left( x \right)u\left( {x,0} \right){\rm{d}}x} = 0
$$

同理

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{{\dot \eta }_1}\left( 0 \right) = - 1.435{v_0}\sqrt {\frac{m}{L}} \\
{{\dot \eta }_2}\left( 0 \right) = - 1.419{v_0}\sqrt {\frac{m}{L}} \\
{{\dot \eta }_3}\left( 0 \right) = - 1.416{v_0}\sqrt {\frac{m}{L}}
\end{array}
$$

解为

$$
\eta_i = \frac {\dot \eta_i(0)} {\omega_i} \sin \omega t
$$

即

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{\eta _1}\left( t \right) = - 0.482m{v_0}\sqrt {\frac{L}{{EA}}} \sin \left( {\omega_1 t} \right)\\
{\eta _2}\left( t \right) = - 0.229m{v_0}\sqrt {\frac{L}{{EA}}} \sin \left( {\omega_2 t} \right)\\
{\eta _3}\left( t \right) = - 0.151m{v_0}\sqrt {\frac{L}{{EA}}} \sin \left( {\omega_3 t} \right)
\end{array}
$$

代入$u\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$即可

## 2.5

将

$$u\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$$

代入可得

$$
m\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} - EA\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} = f\left( {x,t} \right)
$$

同时积分

$$
m\int_0^L {{U_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x} - EA\int_0^L {{U_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{U_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = \int_0^L {{U_j}\left( x \right)f\left( {x,t} \right){\rm{d}}x}
$$

可得

$$
{\ddot \eta _i} + \omega _i^2{\eta _i} = {f_0}{\rm{cos}}\Omega t\int_0^L {{U_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} ,{\rm{ }}i = 1,2,3
$$

解为

$$
\eta_i = \cos \Omega t
$$

即

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{\eta _1}\left( t \right) = \frac{{0.081\sqrt {mL} {f_0}{L^2}}}{{8.851EA - m{\Omega ^2}{L^2}}}\cos \Omega t\\
{\eta _2}\left( t \right) = \frac{{0.018\sqrt {mL} {f_0}{L^2}}}{{38.477EA - m{\Omega ^2}{L^2}}}\cos \Omega t\\
{\eta _3}\left( t \right) = \frac{{0.008\sqrt {mL} {f_0}{L^2}}}{{87.816EA - m{\Omega ^2}{L^2}}}\cos \Omega t
\end{array}
$$

代入$u\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{U_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$即可
